Dialogue: 3,0:00:00.15,0:00:03.84,Callout,,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(640,112)\fs21\c&H00988F8A&}// RETURN TO CALM. CHARCOAL. THE EKG LINE, STEADY NOW
Dialogue: 10,0:00:00.00,0:00:03.69,Caption,,0,0,0,,Here's what Flight 501 leaves on the\Ntable.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:04.03,0:00:07.77,Caption,,0,0,0,,Reliability is not a property a thing\Nhas. It's a
Dialogue: 10,0:00:07.77,0:00:11.51,Caption,,0,0,0,,property of a thing in a situation. Move\Nit somewhere
Dialogue: 10,0:00:11.51,0:00:15.25,Caption,,0,0,0,,new — a faster rocket, a bigger load, a\Ndifferent
Dialogue: 10,0:00:15.25,0:00:18.99,Caption,,0,0,0,,world — and "it's never failed before"\Nstops being a
Dialogue: 10,0:00:18.99,0:00:22.36,Caption,,0,0,0,,promise. It becomes a question you\Nhaven't asked yet.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:22.70,0:00:27.06,Caption,,0,0,0,,The most dangerous code in any system\Nisn't the part
Dialogue: 10,0:00:27.06,0:00:30.56,Caption,,0,0,0,,everyone's watching. It's the part\Neveryone trusts. The
Dialogue: 10,0:00:30.56,0:00:34.48,Caption,,0,0,0,,proven part. The part nobody re-reads,\Nbecause it worked
Dialogue: 10,0:00:34.48,0:00:35.36,Caption,,0,0,0,,last time.
